{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.67\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">一篇詩歌。交給聖詠團長，用絲弦的樂器。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">感恩的詩</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>願上帝憐憫我們，賜福給我們，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">使他的臉向我們發光，（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>好讓全地得知你的道路，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">萬國得知你的救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>上帝啊，願萬民稱謝你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">願萬民都稱謝你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>願萬族都快樂歡呼；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">因為你必按公正審判萬民，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">引導地上的萬族。（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>上帝啊，願萬民稱謝你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">願萬民都稱謝你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>地已經出了土產，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">上帝，我們的上帝，要賜福給我們。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.67.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>上帝要賜福給我們，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">地的四極都要敬畏他！</span></p>\n</div>\n"}